<h2>New!</h2>
<p>Each typeface directory in the repository now includes a vertical metrics table (<code>vertical_metrics.txt</code>).  Combine the data in these reference tables with the new <a href="https://github.com/source-foundry/font-line"><code>font-line</code> tool</a> to modify any font to the line spacing that suits your needs.  Tighten up or keep it loose.</p>
